WEBVTT

00:00:01.080 --> 00:00:02.874
Has anyone here been to Fresno?

00:00:04.417 --> 00:00:05.460
OK, good, good.

00:00:05.793 --> 00:00:06.878
That’s where I’m from,

00:00:06.878 --> 00:00:07.879
where I was born

00:00:07.879 --> 00:00:09.047
and where I live today.

00:00:10.381 --> 00:00:12.425
For those of you less familiar,

00:00:12.425 --> 00:00:15.428
Fresno and the entire
Central Valley of California

00:00:15.428 --> 00:00:18.097
is a place that’s built by agriculture:

00:00:18.097 --> 00:00:21.726
miles and miles of farmland
for as far as the eye can see

00:00:21.726 --> 00:00:25.188
with a couple of large, poor cities
dotting the landscape.

00:00:26.397 --> 00:00:28.816
My family, like much
of the local population,

00:00:28.816 --> 00:00:31.527
is a family of immigrant farm laborers: